    "name": "Tiny Robots: Portal Escape",
    "steam_appid": 3153690,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《小小机器人：传送门逃脱》是一款精彩刺激的3D解谜密室逃脱游戏，背景设定在一个充满奇特角色、色彩缤纷的关卡和异域风情的机器人世界。收集物品，寻找隐藏的线索和线索，解开棘手的机械谜题。哦，别忘了从坏人手中救出你的爷爷！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身为年轻聪明的机器人泰利。一天，当你正走在去爷爷家的路上，却目睹了他被绑架。他的车库一片狼藉，发明也被毁坏，而你唯一能联系到爷爷的只有一台收音机。是谁干的？他们想要什么？你必须解开这个充满烧脑谜题、强大敌人和奇异世界的谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/8a471e7c1c9fd334f53cffc472448872.poster.avif?t=1768381323\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/8a471e7c1c9fd334f53cffc472448872.webm?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/8a471e7c1c9fd334f53cffc472448872.mp4?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过玩披着机器人外衣的经典小游戏，连接不同的机器并破解它们的机制。在我们的街机房间中完成数百个关卡，赢取丰厚奖励。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/dcebc406afe41bfaf6679f4642c37dac.poster.avif?t=1768381323\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/dcebc406afe41bfaf6679f4642c37dac.webm?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/dcebc406afe41bfaf6679f4642c37dac.mp4?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有坏蛋都知道，在各处部署一台威力强大的巨型机器人，能大大提高他们征服世界的计划的成功率。但他们不知道，这只会让你的旅程更具挑战性和乐趣！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/5767c177daec6bbfcde27f0928c52c9a.poster.avif?t=1768381323\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/5767c177daec6bbfcde27f0928c52c9a.webm?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/5767c177daec6bbfcde27f0928c52c9a.mp4?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集隐藏的碎片，在你专属车库里舒适的桌子上将它们组合成神器。精心打造的神器是应对Boss级机器人的必备利器！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/88b986ca1b8f74b6f3d87c0ca4762bd0.poster.avif?t=1768381323\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/88b986ca1b8f74b6f3d87c0ca4762bd0.webm?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3153690/extras/88b986ca1b8f74b6f3d87c0ca4762bd0.mp4?t=1768381323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你非要出手智取敌人，至少要玩得有型。数百种不同的组合，让你随心所欲地定制你的机器人！用鲨鱼头和喷气发动机代替双腿，让你的旅程更加个性化。</p>",
